{"tid":1469422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"決策唔可以情緒化 但要煽動人民情緒","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:26:56.000Z","uid":288030,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b03d93df3adfdd7f6d8bd28a68d26a6b974f810d","tid":1469422,"uid":288030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"唔好因為人哋P牌就block la. 老實講我哋尋日真係有好多事情做得好一般 各位手足我哋要保持情緒控制好 一有咩差錯政府就會轉移視線 大陸嘅文宣會不停loop。<br />\n不過好高興嘅係 我哋尋日有手足由警察手中救翻一個無辜嘅女仔 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住我哋決策唔可以情緒化。但係我哋文宣同埋演繹方式要煽動人民情緒</span></span>"},{"pid":"c17df3df4387ac0ff2e398700e4cc6f4139199a1","tid":1469422,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0b17e746f936a37fcc810dab364e36e46cb295","tid":1469422,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:23.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好心諗野係目標導向，即係每個action都係purpose for五大訴求，而唔好情緒導向啦</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n警犬衰我哋就同佢鬥衰呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地衰唔係我地衰嘅藉口，尤其係鏡頭前面<br />\n<br />\n咁樣只會搞到個普通市民坐上觀壁，反正都係黑狗打白狗，兩隻都係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住呀，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好俾仇恨支配自己</span></strong><br />\n打大劣人出氣係好爽，但之後呢？救得返義士？動私刑只會令好多人失望，更加比藉口清場，可必呢？<br />\n凡事冷靜啲為咗大局着想好冇呀<br />\n<br />\n我地出嚟唔係為咗發洩，係為左五大訴求<br />\n你打佢都唔可能還翻隻眼，倒不如成立獨立調查委員會之後告9開槍果個謀殺仲好啦"},{"pid":"1be5a69a6e7a0c59b19a7c55aafdc40b868ca05a","tid":1469422,"uid":288030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b03d93df3adfdd7f6d8bd28a68d26a6b974f810d","tid":1469422,"uid":288030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"唔好因為人哋P牌就block la. 老實講我哋尋日真係有好多事情做得好一般 各位手足我哋要保持情緒控制好 一有咩差錯政府就會轉移視線 大陸嘅文宣會不停loop。<br />\n不過好高興嘅係 我哋尋日有手足由警察手中救翻一個無辜嘅女仔 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住我哋決策唔可以情緒化。但係我哋文宣同埋演繹方式要煽動人民情緒</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"ad6240c06ebe5452e6fd67f09bb9f99bf8399936","tid":1469422,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"[置頂]睇完今晚機場既事，發現港共真&middot;死穴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468157</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c5cb5ee8d09a332189806fabab199dc0ed6d75f","tid":1469422,"uid":288030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6240c06ebe5452e6fd67f09bb9f99bf8399936","tid":1469422,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"[置頂]睇完今晚機場既事，發現港共真&middot;死穴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468157\" dat